title._content: Captain Story-Martense House, Hallway and Stairs, Church Avenue and East 38th Street, Flatbush, Brooklyn, ca. 1899-1909.

description._content: Daniel Berry Austin (American, born 1863, active 1899-1909). Captain Story-Martense House, Hallway and Stairs, Church Avenue and East 38th Street, Flatbush, Brooklyn, ca. 1899-1909. Dry plate negative. Prints, Drawings and Photographs.
